Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: zimran-logging
Version: 1.2.2
Summary: Loguru, Sentry based logging for FastAPI services
Requires-Python: >=3.10
Description-Content-Type: text/markdown
Requires-Dist: loguru
Requires-Dist: sentry-sdk[fastapi,loguru]

## Installation

```bash
pip install zimran-logging
```

## Usage

```python
from zimran.logging import setup_logger, setup_sentry

setup_logger(debug=...)
setup_sentry(dsn=..., environment=...)
```
